        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>10 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/chat/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🤖</span> Open Lex AI</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">
        What if you had a personal Scrabble coach available around the clock — one that could review your games move by move, drill you on bingos and hooks, find words from any set of tiles, and generate downloadable coaching reports? That coach exists. It's called Lex AI, it lives at <a href="/chat/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">/chat/</a>, and it's completely free. No sign-up. No app download. No premium tier. Just open the page and start improving. This guide walks you through everything Lex can do and how to get the most out of every feature.
      </p>

      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 text-center">
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">LEX AI AT A GLANCE</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 mt-4 flex-wrap">
          <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">Free</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Zero cost, forever</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">Instant</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">No sign-up needed</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">5 games</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Auto-reviews history</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">4 drills</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Dojo training modes</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">PDF</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Coaching reports</p></div>
        </div>
