      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">What Is Lex AI?</h2>

      <p>Lex AI is an AI-powered Scrabble chatbot built directly into ScrabbleWordsFinder.com. Powered by a large language model, it understands Scrabble strategy, word validity, scoring mechanics, and training methodology. Think of it as a coach that lives in your browser — always ready to answer questions, run training drills, review your games, or help you find the perfect word for a tricky rack.</p>

      <p>You access Lex at <a href="/chat/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">/chat/</a>. There is also an "Ask Lex" button available on every page of the site, so you are never more than one click away from coaching. It works on your phone, your tablet, your laptop — any device with a browser. No app to install, no account to create.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ No Sign-Up</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Zero friction. No email, no password, no verification step. Open the page and start chatting within seconds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Always Free</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">No premium tier, no daily limits, no paywall lurking behind advanced features. Every capability is available to every user.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Every Page Access</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">The Ask Lex button appears on every page. Whether you are on the solver, activities, or settings — one click opens your coach.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Mobile Ready</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Fully responsive interface. Train on the bus, review games on the couch, find words at the kitchen table. Works everywhere.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Game History Review — Coaching for Every Activity</h2>

      <p>One of Lex AI's most powerful features is automatic game history review. When you play any of the daily activities on ScrabbleWordsFinder — Word Quiz, Daily Rack Challenge, Daily Anagram, 60-Second Challenge, or Cows and Bulls — your performance data is saved locally. Lex can instantly access that history and provide personalised coaching.</p>

      <p>The workflow is simple: go to the <a href="/activities/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Activities page</a>, find the game panel you want reviewed, and click the Lex coaching button. This takes you directly to <a href="/chat/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">/chat/</a> with your game history pre-loaded. Lex already knows what you played, how you scored, and where you struggled — no copy-pasting or manual entry required.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">⚡ How It Works</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Click the <span class="text-white font-medium">Lex coaching button</span> on any game panel in Activities. It instantly opens <span class="text-white font-medium">/chat/</span> with your history pre-loaded via a context parameter. Lex reads your recent sessions, analyses patterns, and delivers tailored feedback — all within seconds of clicking.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <a href="/chat/?context=quiz" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">🧠</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Word Quiz Review:</span> Lex analyses your quiz accuracy, response timing, and identifies weak vocabulary areas. It spots which word categories trip you up and suggests targeted study lists to close the gaps.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-purple-400 text-xs font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">Review →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/chat/?context=rack" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-amber-400 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">🎲</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-amber-400 font-semibold">Daily Rack Challenge Review:</span> Lex reviews your word choices from the 7-tile rack, compares them against the highest-scoring alternatives you missed, and explains the rack management principles behind optimal plays.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">Review →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/chat/?context=anagram" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-rose-400 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">🔍</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">Daily Anagram Review:</span> Lex reviews your solve times, tracks improvement trends, and hints at letter patterns that help you unscramble words faster. It identifies common anagram shapes you miss.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-rose-400 text-xs font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">Review →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/chat/?context=60sec" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-green-400 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">⏱️</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">60-Second Challenge Review:</span> Lex analyses your pace — words per minute, scoring efficiency, and whether you prioritised short easy words or hunted for high-value finds. It suggests speed strategies tailored to your style.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-green-400 text-xs font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">Review →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/chat/?context=cab" class="block p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-orange-400 transition-colors group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true">🐄</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-orange-400 font-semibold">Cows and Bulls Review:</span> Lex reviews your guess strategies — how efficiently you narrowed down letters, whether you used elimination logic, and how your deduction skills compare to optimal paths.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-orange-400 text-xs font-medium shrink-0 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">Review →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Pro Tip</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">You do not need to navigate to <span class="text-white font-medium">/chat/</span> manually or remember URL parameters. Just click the <span class="text-white font-medium">Lex coaching button</span> on any game panel in the Activities page. The context is loaded automatically — Lex knows exactly which game you want reviewed.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Coaching PDF Reports</h2>

      <p>Lex does not just give you verbal feedback. After analysing your game history, it can generate a structured coaching report that you download as a PDF. These reports break down your performance with clear sections: strengths identified, weaknesses spotted, specific words you should have played, and a practice plan for the coming week.</p>

      <p>You can save up to 5 coaching reports locally in your browser. When the limit is reached, the oldest report is automatically replaced by the newest. If you want to manage your saved reports — view them, delete specific ones, or clear all — visit <a href="/settings/#coaching-reports" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Settings → Coaching Reports 📋</a>.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">🧩 How Coaching PDFs Work</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">1</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Play any game on the Activities page — your results are stored automatically</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">2</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Click the Lex coaching button to open <a href="/chat/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">/chat/</a> with your history pre-loaded</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">3</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Ask Lex to generate a coaching report — it analyses patterns across your sessions</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">4</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Download the PDF or save it locally (up to 5 reports stored)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">5</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Manage your report library at <a href="/settings/#coaching-reports" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">/settings/#coaching-reports</a> 📋</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">📄 PDF Download</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Save the report to your device. Print it, annotate it, share it with your Scrabble club, or review it on the train.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">💾 Local Storage</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Keep up to 5 reports in your browser. Access them anytime without re-generating. Oldest auto-replaced when full.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">The Dojo — Four Training Modes</h2>

      <p>The Dojo is where casual players become competitive ones. It is a dedicated training environment within the Lex chat that offers four structured exercises designed to sharpen the exact skills that separate club players from kitchen-table players. Each exercise targets a different aspect of Scrabble mastery. You can run them in any order, as many times as you want.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎯 Bingo Trainer</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Lex gives you a random bingo-stem rack (7 tiles). Your job: find all valid 7-letter words. Builds the anagramming speed that leads to 50-point bonus plays in real games. The skill that separates 300-point games from 400-point games.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🪝 Hook Quiz</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Given a word on the board, find all valid front hooks and back hooks. Mastering hooks lets you play parallel to existing words and score in multiple directions simultaneously. A must-know skill for tournament play.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🔢 Tile Countdown</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">After N moves have been played, Lex quizzes you on remaining tile counts. This trains the tile-tracking skill that tournament players use to predict opponent racks and make endgame decisions with confidence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
          <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⚖️ Rack Leave Drill</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Lex presents 2-3 possible plays from a rack. You pick which one leaves the best remaining tiles. This is the single most impactful skill for consistent high-level play — the difference between good and great.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🧠 Why Dojo Mode Works</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Deliberate practice beats casual play for improvement. Playing games reinforces existing habits — good and bad. The Dojo <span class="text-white font-medium">isolates individual skills</span> and drills them repeatedly until they become automatic. Ten minutes in the Dojo teaches you more than three casual games. That is how you go from "I know some words" to "I see the board differently."</p>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 bg-indigo-950/10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">📚 Dig Deeper</p>
        <div class="grid gap-2">
          <a href="/blog/bingo-training-methods/" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-900/20 transition-all group">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform shrink-0">→</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors">Bingo Training Methods — systematic approaches to finding 7-letter words faster</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/blog/rack-leave-explained/" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-900/20 transition-all group">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform shrink-0">→</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors">Rack Leave Explained — why what you keep matters more than what you play</span>
